           <p class="answerDisplay_fmt" style="display:none;"> <span class="answerBoxLabel_fmt"> <span class="prompt"> This answer is <span class="answer_text_cor">correct</span>. </span> </span> <br />In addition to causing a skin infection, scratching the chickenpox rash can create open sores, make the rash more severe, and cause scars. </p> 
